# glost-[LANG]-transcription-[SYSTEM]

[SYSTEM] transcription system for [LANGUAGE] language.

## Overview

This package provides the **SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH** for [SYSTEM] transcription rules. It applies [SYSTEM] romanization/transcription to [LANGUAGE] text following the Single Responsibility Principle (SRP).

### Single Responsibility

✅ **Does:**
- Apply [SYSTEM] transcription rules
- Convert [LANGUAGE] text to [SYSTEM] format
- Handle tone markers (if applicable)
- Split into syllables

❌ **Does NOT:**
- Fetch data from databases (use data source packages)
- Query dictionaries (use data source packages)
- Handle other transcription systems (each system is separate)

