## Usage

### Basic Transcription

```typescript
import { transcribeTo[System] } from 'glost-[LANG]-transcription-[SYSTEM]';

const result = transcribeTo[System]("example");
console.log(result.text);      // "[SYSTEM] transcription"
console.log(result.syllables);  // ["syl", "la", "bles"]
```

### With Options

```typescript
